<div class="story">
	<p>Spindrift is a gated community on the ocean front in Corolla with 33 building lots, most of which are already built on. The lots are all large enough to hold a house with an in ground pool. There is an active home owners association which maintains the electronic gate and private roads. You can find Spindrift just past the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/pine-island.asp" title="Pine Island">Pine Island</a> as you travel north on Rte 12 and before you get to the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/ocean-sands.asp" title="Ocean Sands">Ocean Sands</a>.</p>
